                        <h4>Deposit Money</h4>
                        <p>Depositing money into your account is easy and secure. Simply enter the amount you wish to deposit, and your funds will be added to your balance immediately. Ensure that you follow all necessary.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <img src="~/customerSide/assets/images/service_03.jpg" alt="">
                    <div class="down-content">
                        <h4>Transfer Money</h4>
                        <p>Transferring money is a straightforward process that allows you to send funds to another account quickly and securely. Simply enter the recipient's details and the amount you wish to transfer. Ensure you review the transaction details.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
